trans-unit.source: Defines an activity-qualified location that corresponds to an activity status event in the potential execution path of a root workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Definierar en aktivitet kvalificerade plats som motsvarar en aktivitets status händelse i potentiella sökvägen för körningen av en arbetsflödesinstans som rot.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] Whenever the execution status of an activity changes, the workflow instance emits an activity status event to the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]När körningen status för en aktivitet ändras skickar arbetsflödesinstansen en aktivitets status händelse spårning körningsinfrastrukturen.

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure can send the tracking service an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> whenever an activity status event occurs.
trans-unit.target: Spårning körningsinfrastrukturen kan skicka Spårningstjänsten en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>när aktivitetens status händelse inträffar.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>

trans-unit.source: Usually, a tracking service is not interested in every activity status event that occurs in the workflow instance, but only in activity status events associated with certain kinds of activities at specified locations in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Vanligtvis är en spårningstjänst inte intresserad varje aktivitetshändelse status som uppstår i arbetsflödesinstansen, men endast i status aktivitetshändelser som är associerade med vissa typer av aktiviteter på angivna platser i arbetsflödesinstansen.

trans-unit.source: An ActivityTrackingLocation defines the matching parameters for such a location by specifying a reference activity type, a set of activity status change events, and a set of conditions that can more precisely qualify an instance or instances of the reference activity type.
trans-unit.target: En ActivityTrackingLocation definierar matchande parametrar för en sådan plats genom att ange en referenstyp för aktiviteten, en uppsättning aktivitetsstatus ändra händelser och en uppsättning villkor som kan mer exakt kvalificera instanser av referenstyp för aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > A single ActivityTrackingLocation may refer to more than one actual location in the potential execution path of a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > En enda ActivityTrackingLocation kan referera till mer än en faktiska plats i potentiella körning av sökväg för en arbetsflödesinstans.

trans-unit.source: You add ActivityTrackingLocation objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> in order to define the match parameters for an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.
trans-unit.target: Du lägger till ActivityTrackingLocation objekt och <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>för att matcha parametrarna för en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>

trans-unit.source: You must specify the reference activity type to be matched by setting either <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityTypeName%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Du måste ange referenstyp för aktiviteten som ska matchas genom att ange antingen <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityTypeName%2A>eller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityType%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityType%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityTypeName%2A>

trans-unit.source: You may set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.MatchDerivedTypes%2A> to specify interest in activities derived from the reference activity type.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ange <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.MatchDerivedTypes%2A>att ange intresse för aktiviteter som härletts från referensen aktivitetstypen.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.MatchDerivedTypes%2A>

trans-unit.source: You may add <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus> values to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ExecutionStatusEvents%2A> to specify the activity status events to be matched.
trans-unit.target: Du kan lägga till <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>värden till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ExecutionStatusEvents%2A>Anger aktivitetens status för händelser som ska matchas.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ExecutionStatusEvents%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>

trans-unit.source: You may add <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingCondition> objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.Conditions%2A> to specify interest in the reference activity type only for specific conditions.
trans-unit.target: Du kan lägga till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingCondition>objekt till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.Conditions%2A>att ange intresse för aktivitetstypen referens endast för specifika förhållanden.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.Conditions%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingCondition>

trans-unit.source: For example, you can specify interest in only a particular named instance of the reference activity type.
trans-unit.target: Du kan till exempel ange intresse för endast en viss namngiven instans av aktiviteten referenstyp.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the common language runtime (CLR) type of the reference activity to be matched.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den gemensamma språk CLR (runtime) typen för aktiviteten referens som ska matchas.

trans-unit.source: You must specify either the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityTypeName%2A> or ActivityType for the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>.
trans-unit.target: Du måste ange antingen <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityTypeName%2A>ActivityType för <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> eller</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityTypeName%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you want to specify the reference activity type in a version-independent manner, use <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityTypeName%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill ange referenstyp för aktiviteten i ett sätt som är oberoende av versionen Använd <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityTypeName%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityTypeName%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the activity.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>för aktiviteten.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the unqualified name of the reference activity type for the location.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger okvalificerade namn på aktiviteten referenstyp för platsen.

trans-unit.source: You must specify the unqualified name of the reference activity type.
trans-unit.target: Du måste ange icke-kvalificerade namnet på aktiviteten referenstyp.

trans-unit.source: For example, to specify the unqualified name of a <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity> activity set ActivityTypeName to "CodeActivity".
trans-unit.target: Till exempel för att ange icke-kvalificerade namnet på en <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity>aktiviteten ange ActivityTypeName till "CodeActivity".</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity>

trans-unit.source: ActivityTypeName provides a much easier way to specify a reference activity type when you author a profile directly in XML.
trans-unit.target: ActivityTypeName ger ett enklare sätt att ange en referenstyp för aktiviteten när du skapar en profil direkt i XML.

trans-unit.source: ActivityTypeName also provides a version-independent way of referring to a reference activity type.
trans-unit.target: ActivityTypeName innehåller också en version oberoende sätt att hänvisa till en referenstyp för aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: You must specify either the ActivityTypeName or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityType%2A> for the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>.
trans-unit.target: Du måste ange antingen ActivityTypeName eller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityType%2A>för <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The unqualified name of the reference activity type.
trans-unit.target: Icke-kvalificerade namnet på aktiviteten referenstyp.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of conditions that are used to qualify interest in the activity.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en uppsättning villkor som används för att kvalificera intresse för aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: You can use Conditions to more precisely define the instance of the reference activity type to be matched.
trans-unit.target: Du kan använda villkor för att definiera mer exakt instansen av referenstyp för aktiviteten som ska matchas.

trans-unit.source: For example, if you want to match only <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity> activities with an <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Name%2A?displayProperty=fullName> equal to "MyCode", you can set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityTypeName%2A> to"CodeActivity" and add an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingCondition> to Conditions that specifies that the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Name%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of the activity instance must be equal to "MyCode".
trans-unit.target: Om du vill matcha endast exempelvis <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity>aktiviteter med en <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Name%2A?displayProperty=fullName>lika med "MyCode", du kan ange <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityTypeName%2A>till "CodeActivity" och Lägg till en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingCondition>till villkor som anger att den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Name%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen för Aktivitetsinstansen måste vara lika med "MyCode".</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Name%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingCondition> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ActivityTypeName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Name%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity>

trans-unit.source: Every <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingCondition> in Conditions must be `true` and one of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus> values in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ExecutionStatusEvents%2A> must be matched for the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> to be matched.
trans-unit.target: Varje <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingCondition>villkor måste vara `true` och en av de <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>värdena i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ExecutionStatusEvents%2A>måste matchas för den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>som ska matchas.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.ExecutionStatusEvents%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingCondition>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingConditionCollection"></xref> that contains conditions that are used to qualify interest in the activity.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingConditionCollection"> </xref> som innehåller villkor som används för att kvalificera intresse för aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är en tom samling.

trans-unit.source: Gets the list of activity status events that can be matched for this location.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar listan över aktivitetens för statushändelser som kan anpassas för den här platsen.

trans-unit.source: ExecutionStatusEvents specifies the activity status events for which the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> can be matched.
trans-unit.target: ExecutionStatusEvents anger statushändelser aktivitet som den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>kan matchas.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus> values in ExecutionStatusEvents must be matched and every <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingCondition> in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.Conditions%2A> must be `true` for the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> to be matched.
trans-unit.target: En av de <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>värdena i ExecutionStatusEvents måste matchas och varje <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingCondition>i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.Conditions%2A>måste vara `true` för den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>som ska matchas.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation.Conditions%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingCondition> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus>

trans-unit.source: An empty list specifies that no events are to be matched.
trans-unit.target: En tom lista anger att inga händelser som ska matchas.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IList%601> that contains one or more of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IList%601> som innehåller en eller flera av de <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionStatus"> </xref> värden.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty list.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är en tom lista.
